# ─── TinaCloud credentials ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for: npm run build (generates /admin UI) and production content editing
#
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT:
#   1. Copy this file to .env (not version controlled)
#   2. Fill in TINA_CLIENT_ID and TINA_TOKEN below
#
# VERCEL PRODUCTION:
#   1. Add these as environment variables in Vercel dashboard:
#      Settings → Environment Variables
#   2. Set for all environments (Production, Preview, Development)
#   3. Redeploy to apply changes
#
# GETTING CREDENTIALS:
#   1. Sign up free at https://app.tina.io
#   2. Create project → connect GitHub repo (demarci12/klimafirst-claude)
#   3. Go to Settings → API Keys → create read/write token
#
TINA_CLIENT_ID=9024a221-2722-48cf-b4bf-e7f26a2bc930
TINA_TOKEN=

# Git branch TinaCMS should target (auto-detected in Vercel/Netlify)
# GITHUB_BRANCH=main
